prev = abs(x)%10
	x = abs(x)//10
	count = 1
	best = prev
	bestCount = count
	while (x>0):
		current = abs(x)%10

		# Update the current run.
		if current == prev:
			count += 1
		else:
			prev = current
			count = 1

		# Update champion values
		if count==bestCount and best>current:
			best=current

		elif count > bestCount:
			bestCount = count
			best      = current
		x=x//10
	return best
